    "faq-faq": {
      "type": "faq",
      "blocks": {
        "template--19412741194031__9219817a-0b4a-43c6-b3f4-be40ab2b1bf2-1686215539b2ea1459-1": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "item_heading": "1. Overview",
            "text": "<p>This Shipping & Return Policy applies to all purchases made through The EleFant Buy & Sell Back platform at toys.theelefant.ai. By placing an order, you agree to the terms set out below.</p><p>This policy should be read together with our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy.</p>"
          }
        },
        "69788240-769a-49d1-8bfe-19c9284bac08": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "item_heading": "2. Shipping Coverage & Serviceability",
            "text": "<p>The EleFant currently delivers to eighteen (18) or more cities across India. Serviceability for your location can be checked by entering your delivery pincode at checkout.</p><p>If your area is not serviceable, you will be notified before payment is collected. We continually expand our network — please check back periodically.</p>"
          }
        },
        "7ce35cba-4cc3-4de2-8e45-53b2e65f83e7": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "item_heading": "3. Shipping Charges",
            "text": "<p>• Delivery charges, if applicable, are displayed at checkout before you confirm the order.</p><p>• Charges may vary based on delivery location, order value, and promotional offers in effect.</p><p>• Pickup charges for sell-back requests are disclosed upfront when you initiate the sell-back.</p><p>• All shipping and pickup charges are inclusive of applicable taxes unless stated otherwise.</p>"
          }
        },
        "74d3bb51-c5b0-442f-9e35-1d2a241e1f13": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "item_heading": "4. Delivery Timelines",
            "text": "<p>Standard delivery timelines for Buy & Sell Back orders are as follows:</p><p>• <strong>Metro cities:</strong> 2–5 business days from order dispatch.</p><p>• <strong>Non-metro / Tier 2 cities:</strong> 4–7 business days from order dispatch.</p><p>• <strong>Remote locations:</strong> up to 10 business days.</p><p>Actual timelines may vary due to courier performance, weather, public holidays, or unforeseen events. Any delays will be communicated through SMS, email, or in-app notifications.</p>"
          }
        },
        "0a6e6042-4b00-40f3-904b-ce938ad30ed2": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "item_heading": "5. Order Confirmation & Tracking",
            "text": "<p>• Upon successful payment, you will receive an order confirmation via email and SMS.</p><p>• Once dispatched, a tracking link will be shared so you can follow your shipment in real time.</p><p>• Order history and tracking are always accessible from your account dashboard.</p>"
          }
        },
        "f7b1b07d-f2c2-4fbc-b7b5-fbfc8279435e": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "item_heading": "6. Delivery Attempts & Failed Deliveries",
            "text": "<p>Our delivery partners will attempt delivery up to three (3) times at the address provided. If delivery fails due to reasons attributable to the customer — such as incorrect address, unavailability, or refusal to accept — the order may be returned to origin, and re-delivery charges may apply.</p>"
          }
        },
        "1b9e2e36-ef45-4266-87f0-c8af3525b63b": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "item_heading": "7. Returns — Eligibility",
            "text": "<p>A return request will be accepted only if the following conditions are met:</p><p>• The request is raised within <strong>5–7 days from the date of delivery</strong> (exact window as displayed at the time of purchase).</p><p>• The toy is returned unused, in its original condition, with the original packaging, tags, manuals, and all accessories intact.</p><p>• The toy is free from damage, stains, or signs of use beyond minimal handling.</p><p>Toys failing our quality inspection may be rejected for refund or refunded partially at our discretion.</p>"
          }
        },
        "dee602f7-8c63-4ccb-bfb8-801d519d7056": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "item_heading": "8. How to Initiate a Return",
            "text": "<p>• Log in to your account and navigate to “Orders”.</p><p>• Select the order and click “Request Return”.</p><p>• Choose a reason, upload photographs if relevant, and confirm the pickup address.</p><p>• Our logistics partner will schedule a reverse pickup within the next 2–4 business days.</p><p>• Please keep the toy and all accessories packed and ready at the time of pickup.</p>"
          }
        },
        "daf61c64-1525-4c4e-9331-e9b2b6369c60": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "item_heading": "9. Refund Timeline & Method",
            "text": "<p>• Once the returned toy is received and passes quality inspection, refunds are processed within <strong>5–7 business days</strong>.</p><p>• Refunds are issued to the <strong>original payment method</strong> used at the time of purchase.</p><p>• Bank processing timelines (typically 3–7 additional business days) are not within our control.</p><p>• You will receive a confirmation email and SMS once the refund is initiated from our side.</p>"
          }
        },
        "item_RfRxgF": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "item_heading": "10. Non-Returnable Items",
            "text": "<p>The following are not eligible for return or refund:</p><p>• Toys used beyond minimal handling or showing signs of wear.</p><p>• Toys returned without original packaging, manuals, or accessories.</p><p>• Customised, personalised, or made-to-order items (unless defective).</p><p>• Digital vouchers, gift cards, and memberships.</p><p>• Add-ons such as damage waiver, which are non-refundable once purchased.</p><p>If you received a defective or damaged item, please see Section 12 below.</p>"
          }
        },
        "item_8hx4R6": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "item_heading": "11. Sell-Back Pickup (Separate from Returns)",
            "text": "<p>The Sell Back programme is separate from standard returns. Under Sell Back, you can send back a toy you have owned and used at any time — there is no 5–7 day restriction. Once the toy passes our quality check, you receive a <strong>flat 60% of the purchase price</strong> as cash refund or EleFant credit.</p><p>Full terms of the Sell Back programme are set out in our Terms of Service. Pickup is scheduled through your account, and applicable pickup charges (if any) are shown upfront.</p>"
          }
        },
        "item_hD4Mri": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "item_heading": "12. Damaged, Defective, or Missing Items on Delivery",
            "text": "<p>We request that you inspect your package at the time of delivery. If you receive a damaged, defective, or incorrect item:</p><p>• Notify us within <strong>48 hours</strong> of delivery at support@theelefant.ai.</p><p>• Share clear photographs of the item and the packaging.</p><p>• Do not use the item, and preserve all original packaging.</p><p>On verification, we will arrange a free replacement or full refund at your preference.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
